    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Demonschool 恶魔学园》是一款充满新意的战术角色扮演游戏，走位与攻击同样重要。在这里，您将控制菲伊和她那些不合群的伙伴们，体验神秘小岛上的大学生活，同时穿梭于人类世界与恶魔世界之间，消灭那些稀奇古怪的大块头。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1900250/extras/b10d77f0b91e333af6aa0a0fdb57e8c7.webp?t=1769556666\" width=640 height=51 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>战术</strong>：通过连击来消灭敌人。在规划阶段期间，您可以自由撤销您的战略布置。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>故事</strong>：轻恐怖风格的故事，包含大量支线任务。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>时间</strong>：规划您在学校里的日程安排，为您的角色升级，强化他们的技能。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>友谊</strong>：您可以与多达15名角色建立友谊的纽带。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1900250/extras/a3b797d8cfd6bdece5bff625c54c63cb.webp?t=1769556666\" width=640 height=51 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1900250/extras/7fb62070b034e9ebb2aa8cb9255da1bf.poster.avif?t=1769556666\" width=640 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1900250/extras/7fb62070b034e9ebb2aa8cb9255da1bf.webm?t=1769556666\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1900250/extras/7fb62070b034e9ebb2aa8cb9255da1bf.mp4?t=1769556666\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏中的单位会与环境产生相互作用。 敌人可能会被卡住，物件可能会被挪动，部分角色还会横冲直撞。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1900250/extras/9cb9742de300472232a7ab3e59122354.poster.avif?t=1769556666\" width=640 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1900250/extras/9cb9742de300472232a7ab3e59122354.webm?t=1769556666\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1900250/extras/9cb9742de300472232a7ab3e59122354.mp4?t=1769556666\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在规划阶段，按照您自己的节奏进行规划，之后将其全部执行。此外，在规划阶段期间，您可以自由撤销您的战略布置。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1900250/extras/7926293d5203a1013a35d0b6824b77ae.poster.avif?t=1769556666\" width=640 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1900250/extras/7926293d5203a1013a35d0b6824b77ae.webm?t=1769556666\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1900250/extras/7926293d5203a1013a35d0b6824b77ae.mp4?t=1769556666\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>强化</i>友军，<i>削弱</i>敌人，进一步强化伤害输出。 记得留意伤害数值！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1900250/extras/c89917570521e0fb800217eecdb5dd14.poster.avif?t=1769556666\" width=640 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1900250/extras/c89917570521e0fb800217eecdb5dd14.webm?t=1769556666\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1900250/extras/c89917570521e0fb800217eecdb5dd14.mp4?t=1769556666\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用连击造成高额伤害，同时触发独特的元素攻击。您可以利用这些机制来攻击敌人的弱点。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1900250/extras/27e0ba187a44c4db83b114c73100e0d3.webp?t=1769556666\" width=640 height=51 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1900250/extras/fee53cdaa5f582a9cf80aef629d5f417.avif?t=1769556666\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1900250/extras_big/fee53cdaa5f582a9cf80aef629d5f417.avif?t=1769556666 width=800 height=1091 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1900250/extras/e2977bb9b96da4bf1ba64f7cbcde9e51.webp?t=1769556666\" width=640 height=51 /></span>探索神秘的小岛，在大学生涯日复一日、周复一周的日子里，慢慢揭开这座小岛神秘的面纱。规划队伍的日程安排，强化队员的技能，帮助他们获得新的能力。 根据您在游戏中的选择获得新的队友，增进队伍成员之间的关系。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1900250/extras/09d5ecb1df382967d5148e706d962c8c.avif?t=1769556666\" width=640 height=480 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1900250/extras/3a15263c0e7bd70348840251ee004c5d.avif?t=1769556666\" width=640 height=480 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1900250/extras/53b2e9d4f9c3c5b43e12edf2557f3c86.avif?t=1769556666\" width=640 height=480 /></span></p>",
